defaultI do feel it is appropriate and relevant that the end of life care services are not forgotten within the context of managing long term conditions.
default 
defaultIt is often very difficult for our health clinicians to provide an accurate pr
defaultognosis of life expectancy.
default 
defaultWe
default will be informed that an individual has only a short period of life, when on many occasions individuals survive long after their prognosis.
