defaultThere are an increasing number of people surviving longer because of improved health and social care services.
default 
defaultThis 
defaultmeans
default care services are managing a long-term condition whereby their life expectancy was determined to be short. 
defaultIn addition it is important to recognise that many people who have a long term condition are nearing the end of their life.
